    "name": "Craftia Regency",
    "steam_appid": 3269440,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>欢迎来到克拉夫蒂亚摄政酒店！</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >沉浸在平静的图案和优雅的设计世界中，灵感来自摄政时代的优雅和魅力！ Craftia 非常适合缓解压力、享受创意休息或作为自我表达的出口。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >给你自己的手持风扇上色，制作独特的书籍封面，或者用可爱的鲜花和丝带制作你自己的下午茶套装。有无限的可能性！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3269440/extras/fc5a50d844db49562ad1684b8af2338e.avif?t=1768965581\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3269440/extras_big/fc5a50d844db49562ad1684b8af2338e.avif?t=1768965581 width=800 height=258 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3269440/extras/635c45808f6cb56f37631b15f3661756.avif?t=1768965581\" width=616 height=80 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >着色是 Craftia 的核心，其设计目的是让用户超级满意。主要着色笔模仿记号笔的手感和完美度。 Craftia 拥有金属色、哑光和闪亮的着色笔，是每个调色师的梦想！ </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >无论您是经验丰富的艺术家还是初学者，Craftia 都提供了一系列设计，您可以按照自己的节奏进行探索。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >使用您的鼠标或任何类型的绘图板开始您与 Craftia 的着色冒险！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3269440/extras/7e391fa224b6928c637b671361e142fd.poster.avif?t=1768965581\" width=608 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3269440/extras/7e391fa224b6928c637b671361e142fd.webm?t=1768965581\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3269440/extras/7e391fa224b6928c637b671361e142fd.mp4?t=1768965581\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3269440/extras/36865aea587df19e95d4cf7c1c64e6cd.avif?t=1768965581\" width=616 height=80 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在您自己的修道院中展示您的作品！每个房间的配色方案和氛围都可以完全定制。一天中有不同的季节和时间。随意使用轻松的氛围作为学习时的背景或截图作为桌面壁纸！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3269440/extras/9c8f34a8b76057d03cd5e787d9caba6a.poster.avif?t=1768965581\" width=608 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3269440/extras/9c8f34a8b76057d03cd5e787d9caba6a.webm?t=1768965581\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3269440/extras/9c8f34a8b76057d03cd5e787d9caba6a.mp4?t=1768965581\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3269440/extras/ca73150111cdcd8e59f0237201ecfc98.avif?t=1768965581\" width=616 height=80 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >疯狂吧！使用贴纸和效果笔，超越着色的范畴，充分享受 Craftia 的乐趣。制作奢华的蛋糕、奢华的刺绣等等！亮片、珠子和宝石会让你的刺绣闪闪发光。还有更多东西有待发现！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3269440/extras/7f0218cfae9dadaf3960191a08dad3b1.poster.avif?t=1768965581\" width=608 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3269440/extras/7f0218cfae9dadaf3960191a08dad3b1.webm?t=1768965581\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3269440/extras/7f0218cfae9dadaf3960191a08dad3b1.mp4?t=1768965581\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3269440/extras/6efee1da6e5cfee79398e6092db6d702.avif?t=1768965581\" width=616 height=80 /></span>该游戏是一位独立开发者的热情项目。您可以联系我并分享您的反馈和想法！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3269440/extras/306acd6547f80f09a765cc25d95fdb94.poster.avif?t=1768965581\" width=608 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3269440/extras/306acd6547f80f09a765cc25d95fdb94.webm?t=1768965581\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3269440/extras/306acd6547f80f09a765cc25d95fdb94.mp4?t=1768965581\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
